Allright. I'm kinda awake now. I'll give posting a shot :-)

::Zardus::

Zardus looks at Orchestra, wondering for a second why the Predacon had wanted to talk to him.

"Well, lets not waste time, shall we? I'm assuming you came here in the interests of peace."

As he talks, his comm replies to Composer, unheard to Orchestra (unless he intercepts it, I guess). "Yes. Please report to my position. I'm in a meeting, but you can sit through it."




--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Abyssian Badass" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra/Composer::
> 
>     Orchestra sat himself down.  He had the Infectrons bugging him on his
> mind, but he tried to think of the peace talks.  Orchestra had his finger
> tips touching, ready to start the discussion.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>      Meanwhile, Composer was standing around, waiting for Zardus'
> reply(sorry if I didn't get your reply to this old post).
> 
>      "Leader, do you still wish for me to accompany you somewhere?" Composer
> asked through his comm-link.
